'''赛日·甘斯布'''（{{lang-fr|'''Serge Gainsbourg'''}}，原名'''Lucien Ginsburg'''<ref>[[Ginsburg|Ginsburg]] is sometimes spelled Ginzburg in the media, including print encyclopedias and dictionaries. However, Ginsburg is the name engraved on [[:Image:Serge_Gainsbourg_Grave.jpg|Gainsbourg's grave]], and "Lucien Ginsburg" is the name by which Gainsbourg is referred to, as a performer, in the [[Société_des_auteurs,_compositeurs_et_éditeurs_de_musique|Sacem]] catalog [http://www.sacem.fr/catel/] {{Wayback|url=http://www.sacem.fr/catel/ |date=20120414002952 }} (along with "Serge Gainsbourg" as the author/composer/adaptor)</ref>，{{IPA-fr|sɛʁʒ ɡɛ̃sbuʁ}}，{{bd|1928年|4月2日|1991年|3月2日|catIdx=G}}）<ref name=ALLMUSIC>[{{Allmusic|class=artist|id=p22806/biography|pure_url=yes}} allmusic Biography]</ref>，法国歌手、作曲家、钢琴家、电影作曲家、诗人、画家、编剧、作家、演员和导演。<ref>Obituary ''[[Variety_Obituaries|Variety]]'', 11 March 1991.</ref>他是法国流行音乐中最重要的人物之一，作品常充满挑衅性和诽谤性，<ref>{{cite web |last=Ankeny |first=Jason |url=http://www.allmusic.com/artist/serge-gainsbourg-mn0000174822 |title=Serge Gainsbourg – Music Biography, Credits and Discography |publisher=AllMusic |date= |accessdate=2012-11-10 |archive-date=2017-11-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171102111825/https://www.allmusic.com/artist/serge-gainsbourg-mn0000174822 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="simmons2001">{{cite news | url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2001/feb/02/culture.features | work=The Guardian | first=Sylvie | last=Simmons | title=An extract from Serge Gainsbourg: A Fistful of Gitanes by Sylvie Simmons | date=2001-02-02 | accessdate=2014-07-24 | archive-date=2012-02-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120222204841/http://www.guardian.co.uk/books/2001/feb/02/culture.features | dead-url=no }}</ref>他的曲风多元，体现了[[爵士乐|爵士]]，曼波（manbo），[[世界音乐|世界]]，[[香颂|香颂]]，[[流行_(音樂類型)|流行]]和[[yé-yé|yé-yé]]，到[[摇滚|摇滚]]，[[前衛搖滾|前衛搖滾]]，[[雷鬼音樂|雷鬼]]，[[電子音樂|電子]]，[[迪斯科|迪斯科]]，[[新浪潮|新浪潮]]和[[放克|放克]]等各种风格。甘斯布多样的音乐风格和个性使他难以被归类，他的作品已深入人心，被视为世界上最有影响力的流行音乐家之一。<ref>{{cite web |author=2003年4月21日 (月) |url=http://www.hmv.co.jp/news/newsDetail.asp?newsnum=304080038 |title=The 100 Greatest Artists – No. 62 |publisher=Hmv.co.jp |date= |accessdate=2011-01-25 |archive-date=2011-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110516075523/http://www.hmv.co.jp/news/newsDetail.asp?newsnum=304080038 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

他的抒情作品经常因为挑衅，幽默，讽刺或颠覆的原因加入大量巧妙的文字游戏来欺骗听众。他歌曲中的文字游戏常见类型有[[擬聲詞|擬聲詞]]，[[押韻|押韻]]，[[首音互換|首音互換]]和[[雙關語|雙關語]]等等。在甘斯布的职业生涯中，他写了超过500首歌曲。<ref>{{link-fr|赛日·甘斯布歌曲列表|Liste des chansons de Serge Gainsbourg}}</ref><ref>{{link-fr|赛日·甘斯布的重复小调|Reprises des chansons de Serge Gainsbourg}}</ref>

==早期生活==
甘斯布出生于法国巴黎，是俄罗斯犹太移民的儿子<ref>Benjamin Ivry: [http://forward.com/articles/14621/the-man-with-the-yellow-star-/ The Man With the Yellow Star: The Jewish Life of Serge Gainsbourg] {{Wayback|url=http://forward.com/articles/14621/the-man-with-the-yellow-star-/ |date=20150225001247 }}, ''The Jewish Daily Forward'', 26 November 2008.</ref><ref>[http://www.deconstruction-in-music.com/proefschrift/500_john_zorn/580_great_jewish_music/great_jewish_music.html Great Jewish Music] {{Wayback|url=http://www.deconstruction-in-music.com/proefschrift/500_john_zorn/580_great_jewish_music/great_jewish_music.html |date=20200510013248 }}, Deconstruction in Music.</ref>。父母在[[1917年俄国革命|1917年俄国革命]]后逃到巴黎。他的父亲是一个古典音乐家，工作是在赌场或者夜总会弹钢琴。也教他和双胞胎妹妹<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.notablebiographies.com/supp/Supplement-Fl-Ka/Gainsbourg-Serge.html |title=Serge Gainsbourg Biography – life, family, parents, name, story, death, wife, school, young, son, book, old, born, husband, marriage, time, year, scandal, sister, The outsider |publisher=Notablebiographies.com |date= |accessdate=2011-01-25 |archive-date=2021-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307000310/https://www.notablebiographies.com/supp/Supplement-Fl-Ka/Gainsbourg-Serge.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|author=LucienGrix No real name given + Add Contact |url=https://secure.flickr.com/photos/48580880@N08/4443395660/ |title=1928 Liliane & Lucien Ginsburg | Flickr – Photo Sharing! |publisher=Flickr |date= |accessdate=2011-01-25}}</ref>弹钢琴。<ref>http://www.vanityfair.com {{Wayback|url=http://www.vanityfair.com/ |date=20110528014639 }}, Robinson, Lisa,  Legends, “''The World of Serge Gainsbourg'',” November, 2007, retrieved September 3, 2012</ref>

==个人生活==
1951年11月3日他与Elisabeth "Lize" Levitsky开始第一段婚姻，1957年离婚。1964年1月7日与Françoise-Antoinette "Béatrice" Pancrazzi结婚，与第二任妻子有两个孩子：女儿Natacha（出生于1964年8月8日）和儿子Paul（出生于1968年春）。他们于1966年2月离婚。

1967年末，他与[[碧姬·芭杜|碧姬·芭杜]]有一段简短而热烈的恋情，为芭杜制作了歌曲和专辑。

1968年中，他爱上了年轻的英国歌手和女星[[珍·柏金|珍·柏金]]，他们的关系维持了十多年<ref name="Charlotte">{{Cite news |work=TIME |title=French Chanteuse Charlotte Gainsbourg |url=http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1956411,00.html#ixzz1Va7NJr9U |first=William Lee |last=Adams |date=2010-01-26 |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2013-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130817082155/http://www.time.com/time/arts/article/0,8599,1956411,00.html#ixzz1Va7NJr9U |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1971年，他们有了一个女儿，女演员和歌手[[夏洛特·甘斯柏格|夏洛特·甘斯柏格]]。虽然许多消息来源称，他们已经结婚<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.life.com/gallery/44901/image/2661198/best-looking-couples-ever#index/2 |title=Best-Looking Couples Ever |work=LIFE.com |publisher=See Your World LLC }}{{Dead link|date=2020年4月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}<br>{{Cite news |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/travel/europe/inside-travel-pooches-in-paris-2309010.html |title=Inside Travel: Pooches in Paris |date=2011-07-09 |author=JoAnne Good |publisher=independent.co.uk |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115231704/https://www.independent.co.uk/travel/europe/inside-travel-pooches-in-paris-2309010.html |dead-url=no }}<br>{{Cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/8309301/Serge-Gainsbourgs-women-the-music.html |title=Serge Gainsbourg's women: the music |date=2011-02-07 |publisher=Telegraph Media Group Limited |work=The Telegraph |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308151540/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/8309301/Serge-Gainsbourgs-women-the-music.html |dead-url=no }}<br>{{Cite news |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/gainsbourg-the-movie/birkin-bardot |title=Birkin, Bardot and Gainsbourg, the accidental sex symbol |publisher=Guardian News and Media Limited |work=The Guardian |date=2010-07-05 |accessdate=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2012-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120616195829/http://www.guardian.co.uk/gainsbourg-the-movie/birkin-bardot |dead-url=no }}<br>{{cite web |url=http://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/jane-birkin/id45830 |title=Jane Birkin |publisher=Apple Inc |access-date=2014-07-24 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205013013/http://itunes.apple.com/us/artist/jane-birkin/id45830 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但他们的女儿夏洛特透露，情况并非如此。<ref name="Charlotte"/>柏金1980年离开甘斯布。

他最后的伴侣是Bambou（[[弗里德里希·保盧斯|弗里德里希·保盧斯]]元帅的侄孙女）。1986年，他们有了一个儿子Lucien。

